ontent_rendered":"<p>看了下商店里，一共三个，一个是标准的，一个是 HD 版，一个是图标蓝色的测试版</p>\n<p>标准版，看视频，感觉温度会飙很高，比如现在季节，我看网页什么的，温度也就 24 度左右，但是开了哔哩哔哩这个客户端，看视频，温度马上就飙到 50 多度了</p>\n<p>HD 版 默认字体太小，也没找到哪里能调，温度好像比标准版好，可能是适配 M1 比较好。</p>\n<p>测试版的界面就是手机的竖屏方式，即便最大化，也只是放大，字体是大了，但是显示内容不如前两个多。比较别扭。温度感觉是最低的。</p>\n<p>话说现在 M1 上的客户端，b 站，抖音，微博什么的，这个音量都不能单独设置。只能把系统音量拉到很低，才能接受。否则音量太大了，特别是外接音箱的话简直了。</p>\n","last_modified":1641518897,"replies":12,"id":826722},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1628872984","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1628872984","title":"分享发现","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","topics":34869,"footer":"","header":"分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。","title_alternative":"Share","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1628872984","stars":4697,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":16,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":233897,"username":"NowTime","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/NowTime","website":"https://nowtime.cc","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"PrintNow","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7522/6912/233897_mini.png?m=1637981887","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7522/6912/233897_normal.png?m=1637981887","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7522/6912/233897_large.png?m=1637981887","created":1496591110,"last_modified":1637981887},"last_reply_by":"7gugu","last_touched":1641521252,"title":"粤核酸是什么操作，一搜有那么多个","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/826717","created":1641518034,"deleted":0,"content":"![Screenshot_2022-01-07-09-11-43-400_com.tencent.mm.jpg]( https://s2.loli.net/2022/01/07/JRY1EXHWPmDCsBp.jpg)","content_rendered":"<p><img alt=\"Screenshot_2022-01-07-09-11-43-400_com.tencent.mm.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2022/01/07/JRY1EXHWPmDCsBp.jpg\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1641518064,"replies":12,"id":826717},{"node":{"avatar_l